{"title":"Individual Vehicle Approval (IVA): list of technical services","public_updated_at":"2015-03-05T11:22:53Z","details":{"body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><h2 id=\"technical-services\">Technical services</h2>\n\n<p>This list provides details of authorised designated tehnical service providers for <abbr title=\"Individual Vehicle Approval\">IVA</abbr> testing.</p>\n\n<p>You need to use this list if youâ€™ve to pay for your own <abbr title=\"Individual Vehicle Approval\">IVA</abbr> tests to be carried out.</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"jlr-product-compliance-centre-emission-test-laboratory\">JLR Product Compliance Centre Emission Test Laboratory</h3>\n\n<div class=\"address\"><div class=\"adr org fn\"><p>\n\nProduct Compliance Centre  \n<br>Emission Test Laboratory  \n<br>Landrover  \n<br>Lode Lane  \n<br>Solihull  \n<br>B92 8NW\n<br>\n</p></div></div>\n\n<p>Contact: John Hanson<br>\nTelephone: 0121 700 3131<br>\nEmail: <a href=\"mailto:jhanso14@jaguarlandrover.com\">jhanso14@jaguarlandrover.com</a></p>\n\n<h4 id=\"items-tested\">Items tested</h4>\n\n<p>This technical service tests:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>emissions</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3 id=\"millbrook-proving-ground-ltd\">Millbrook Proving Ground Ltd</h3>\n\n<div class=\"address\"><div class=\"adr org fn\"><p>\n\nMillbrook  \n<br>Near Ampthill  \n<br>Bedford  \n<br>MK45 2JQ\n<br>\n</p></div></div>\n\n<p>Contact:Tony Soper<br>\nTelephone: 01525 408354<br>\nFax: 01525 408459<br>\nEmail: <a href=\"mailto:tony.soper@millbrook.co.uk\">tony.soper@millbrook.co.uk</a></p>\n\n<h4 id=\"items-tested-1\">Items tested</h4>\n\n<p>This technical service tests:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>noise</li>\n  <li>emissions</li>\n  <li>brakes</li>\n  <li>seat belt anchorages</li>\n  <li>front and side impacts</li>\n  <li>protective steering</li>\n  <li>anti-theft device</li>\n  <li>CO2/fuelconsumption</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3 id=\"mira-ltd\">MIRA Ltd</h3>\n\n<div class=\"address\"><div class=\"adr org fn\"><p>\n\nWatling Street  \n<br>Nuneaton  \n<br>Warwickshire  \n<br>CV10 0TU\n<br>\n</p></div></div>\n\n<p>Contact: Richard Whiting<br>\nTelephone: 02476 355 482<br>\nEmail: <a href=\"mailto:richard.whiting@mira.co.uk\">richard.whiting@mira.co.uk</a></p>\n\n<h4 id=\"items-tested-2\">Items tested</h4>\n\n<p>This technical service tests:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>noise</li>\n  <li>emissions (excluding 4x4 diesel emissions)</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3 id=\"status\">STATUS</h3>\n\n<div class=\"address\"><div class=\"adr org fn\"><p>\n\nSchool of Engineering  \n<br>Manchester Metropolitan University  \n<br>Chester Street  \n<br>Manchester  \n<br>M1 5GD\n<br>\n</p></div></div>\n\n<p>Contact: Michael Hughes<br>\nTelephone: 0161 247 6240<br>\nEmail: <a href=\"mailto:m.p.hughes@mmu.ac.uk\">m.p.hughes@mmu.ac.uk</a></p>\n\n<h4 id=\"items-tested-3\">Items tested</h4>\n\n<p>This technical service tests:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>seat belt anchorages</li>\n</ul>\n\n</div>","headings":"<ol class=\"unnumbered\"><li><a href=\"#technical-services\">Technical services</a></li></ol>","public_timestamp":"2015-03-05T13:44:07.000+00:00","first_published_version":false},"routes":[{"path":"/government/publications/finding-an-authorised-technical-service-for-iva/finding-an-authorised-technical-service-for-iva","type":"exact"}],"redirects":[],"publishing_app":"whitehall","rendering_app":"government-frontend","need_ids":[],"phase":"live","analytics_identifier":null,"document_type":"html_publication","schema_name":"html_publication","first_published_at":"2016-10-20T15:23:33Z","base_path":"/government/publications/finding-an-authorised-technical-service-for-iva/finding-an-authorised-technical-service-for-iva","description":null,"content_id":"d06ede40-a591-4dc0-9a62-62a94a4755ce","locale":"en","expanded_links":{"organisations":[{"analytics_identifier":"EA570","api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/driver-and-vehicle-standards-agency","base_path":"/government/organisations/driver-and-vehicle-standards-agency","content_id":"d39237a5-678b-4bb5-a372-eb2cb036933d","description":nul